      <title>伊姆兰·汗的缺席加剧了巴基斯坦选民的反抗和绝望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/pakistan-election-with-imran-khan-in-jail-military-influence-weighs-on-voters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在巴基斯坦第二大城市拉合尔，伊姆兰·汗领导的政党陷入困境，其竞选办公室的工作人员仍然对本周晚些时候的选举持挑衅态度，尽管这位前总理已入狱，而另一位前领导人纳瓦兹·谢里夫是最有可能当选的人。掌权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/pakistan-election-with-imran-khan-in-jail-military-influence-weighs-on-voters</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
