    <item>
      <title>奥夫拉多尔推出一系列改革措施以压制反对派，激发基础</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/amlo-unveils-slew-of-reforms-to-corner-opposition-energize-base</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩兹·奥夫拉多尔周一公布了一系列针对养老金、工人工资和最高法院的长期宪法改革，此举似乎是为了在六月选举前激励他的支持者并引诱反对派。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/amlo-unveils-slew-of-reforms-to-corner-opposition-energize-base</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 01:01:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>震动韩国政坛的迪奥包“丑闻”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/south-korea-s-dior-bag-scandal-why-uproar-over-first-lady-is-shaking-politics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一段秘密录制的视频据称显示韩国第一夫人金建熙收到了一个豪华手提包，这在关键选举前几个月削弱了公众对总统尹淑烈的支持。这是围绕第一夫人的一系列争议中的最新一起，她打破了传统，在总统事务和尹竞选活动中发挥了重要作用。尹尚未对此事发表正式评论，预计将在周三的电视采访中解决此事]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/south-korea-s-dior-bag-scandal-why-uproar-over-first-lady-is-shaking-politics</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 00:45:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>妮基·哈利 (Nikki Haley) 在受到威胁后请求特勤局提供保护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/nikki-haley-requests-secret-service-protection-after-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据她的竞选团队称，妮基·黑莉(Nikki Haley)已请求特勤局提供保护，理由是她作为唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)总统提名的最后一位主要共和党挑战者而受到威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/nikki-haley-requests-secret-service-protection-after-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 00:37:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国官员敦促哥伦比亚与委内瑞拉反对派接触</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/us-officials-urge-colombia-to-engage-with-venezuela-opposition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着委内瑞拉政治僵局加剧，拜登政府高级官员敦促哥伦比亚总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗周二与委内瑞拉反对派接触，从而使取消制裁以换取自由公平投票的协议面临风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/us-officials-urge-colombia-to-engage-with-venezuela-opposition</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 00:27:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞内加尔立法者同意总统投票推迟 10 个月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/senegal-lawmakers-approve-ten-month-delay-to-presidential-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞内加尔立法者同意将总统投票推迟 10 个月，以便议会对选举可能参加选举的候选人的过程进行调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/senegal-lawmakers-approve-ten-month-delay-to-presidential-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 23:09:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于共和党的怀疑，美国边境-乌克兰援助协议在参议院几近崩溃</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/senate-s-border-ukraine-deal-faces-increasingly-bleak-prospects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项艰难达成的两党协议，即实施新的美国边境限制和解锁乌克兰战争援助，在参议院正处于崩溃的边缘，面对共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普的反对，共和党的支持崩溃了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/senate-s-border-ukraine-deal-faces-increasingly-bleak-prospects</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 22:56:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
